{"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI","doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Divider"]]},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Divider\/transaction(_:)","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"metadata":{"platforms":[{"name":"iOS","deprecated":false,"unavailable":false,"beta":false,"introducedAt":"13.0"},{"name":"macOS","deprecated":false,"unavailable":false,"beta":false,"introducedAt":"10.15"},{"name":"tvOS","deprecated":false,"unavailable":false,"beta":false,"introducedAt":"13.0"},{"name":"visionOS","deprecated":false,"unavailable":false,"beta":false,"introducedAt":"1.0"},{"name":"watchOS","deprecated":false,"unavailable":false,"beta":false,"introducedAt":"6.0"}],"role":"symbol","symbolKind":"method","modules":[{"name":"OpenSwiftUI","relatedModules":["OpenSwiftUICore"]}],"externalID":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore4ViewPAAE11transactionyQryAA11TransactionVzcF::SYNTHESIZED::s:11OpenSwiftUI7DividerV","fragments":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"transaction","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"((","kind":"text"},{"text":"inout","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Transaction","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore11TransactionV"},{"text":") -> ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Void","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:s4Voida"},{"text":") -> ","kind":"text"},{"text":"some","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"View","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore4ViewP"}],"title":"transaction(_:)","extendedModule":"OpenSwiftUICore","remoteSource":{"url":"https:\/\/github.com\/OpenSwiftUIProject\/OpenSwiftUI\/blob\/main\/Sources\/OpenSwiftUICore\/Animation\/Transaction\/TransactionModifier.swift#L84","fileName":"TransactionModifier.swift"},"roleHeading":"Instance Method"},"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"Applies the given transaction mutation function to all animations used","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"within the view.","type":"text"}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/openswiftui\/divider\/transaction(_:)"]}],"sections":[],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"attribute","text":"nonisolated"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"transaction"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"_"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"transform"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"@escaping"},{"kind":"text","text":" ("},{"kind":"keyword","text":"inout"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Transaction","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore11TransactionV","text":"Transaction"},{"kind":"text","text":") -> "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:s4Voida","text":"Void"},{"kind":"text","text":") -> "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"some"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/View","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore4ViewP","text":"View"},{"kind":"text","text":"\n"}],"languages":["swift"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"parameters":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The transformation to apply to transactions"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"within this view."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"transform"}],"kind":"parameters"},{"content":[{"text":"Return Value","type":"heading","anchor":"return-value","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"A view that wraps this view and applies a transformation to"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"all transactions used within the view."}]}],"kind":"content"},{"content":[{"level":2,"text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Use this modifier to change or replace the animation used in a view."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Consider three identical animations controlled by a"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"button that executes all three animations simultaneously:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The first animation rotates the “Rotation” ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Text","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" view by 360","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"degrees.","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The second uses the ","type":"text"},{"code":"transaction(_:)","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" modifier to change the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"animation by adding a delay to the start of the animation","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"by two seconds and then increases the rotational speed of the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"“Rotation\\nModified” ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Text","type":"reference"},{"text":" view animation by a factor of 2.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The third animation uses the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"transaction(_:)"},{"text":" modifier to","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"replace the rotation animation affecting the “Animation\\nReplaced”","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Text"},{"text":" view with a spring animation.","type":"text"}]}]}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The following code implements these animations:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["struct TransactionExample: View {","    @State private var flag = false","","    var body: some View {","        VStack(spacing: 50) {","            HStack(spacing: 30) {","                Text(\"Rotation\")","                    .rotationEffect(Angle(degrees:","                                            self.flag ? 360 : 0))","","                Text(\"Rotation\\nModified\")","                    .rotationEffect(Angle(degrees:","                                            self.flag ? 360 : 0))","                    .transaction { view in","                        view.animation =","                            view.animation?.delay(2.0).speed(2)","                    }","","                Text(\"Animation\\nReplaced\")","                    .rotationEffect(Angle(degrees:","                                            self.flag ? 360 : 0))","                    .transaction { view in","                        view.animation = .interactiveSpring(","                            response: 0.60,","                            dampingFraction: 0.20,","                            blendDuration: 0.25)","                    }","            }","","            Button(\"Animate\") {","                withAnimation(.easeIn(duration: 2.0)) {","                    self.flag.toggle()","                }","            }","        }","    }","}"]},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Use this modifier on leaf views such as ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Image","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" or ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Button","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" rather","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"than container views such as ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/VStack","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" or ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/HStack","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":". The","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"transformation applies to all child views within this view; calling","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"code":"transaction(_:)","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" on a container view can lead to unbounded scope of","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"execution depending on the depth of the view hierarchy.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"references":{"doc://OpenSwiftUI/documentation/OpenSwiftUI/Text":{"kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Text","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/openswiftui\/text","type":"topic","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"Text","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"Text","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Text","abstract":[]},"doc://OpenSwiftUI/documentation/OpenSwiftUI/Transaction":{"type":"topic","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"Transaction","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"Transaction","url":"\/documentation\/openswiftui\/transaction","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Transaction","abstract":[{"text":"The context of the current state-processing update.","type":"text"}],"role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Transaction","kind":"identifier"}]},"doc://OpenSwiftUI/documentation/OpenSwiftUI/Divider/transaction(_:)":{"role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Divider\/transaction(_:)","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Applies the given transaction mutation function to all animations used"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"within the view."}],"url":"\/documentation\/openswiftui\/divider\/transaction(_:)","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword